abPOA
------------------------------------------
SIMD-based C library for fast partial order alignment using adaptive band

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libabpoa-devel-1.5.3-1bl1
  libabpoa1-1.5.3-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.0-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/yangao07/abPOA

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/yangao07/abPOA/archive/refs/tags/v1.5.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack abPOA-1.5.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./abPOA-1.5.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/abPOA-1.5.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/abPOA-1.5.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libabpoa1-1.5.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libabpoa-devel-1.5.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(abPOA)
  /usr/bin/abpoa.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/abPOA.README
  /usr/share/doc/abPOA/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/abPOA/README.md

(libabpoa1)
  /usr/bin/cygabpoa-1.dll

(libabpoa-devel)
  /usr/include/abpoa.h
  /usr/include/simd_instruction.h
  /usr/lib/libabpoa.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/abpoa-1.pc

------------------

